headline.main: Pentagon Leaves Open Possibility of More North Korea Launch Attempts
headline.print_headline: Pentagon Leaves Open Possibility of More North Korea Launch Attempts

lead_paragraph: The U.S. military on Monday left open the possibility of additional North Korean ballistic missile launch attempts beyond the four medium-range missiles that landed in the sea off northwest Japan.
